literally a guiding light in my world.

26
00:02:40,827 --> 00:02:43,796
And he completes me.

27
00:02:46,533 --> 00:02:49,798
There's no reason
to lament for being blind.

28
00:02:50,937 --> 00:02:54,896
You know what
