under the one condition
that she's blind!

101
00:12:44,029 --> 00:12:46,395
Never do I enjoy
her being blind, but...

102
00:12:47,533 --> 00:12:48,795
How bittersweet!

103
00:12:49,735 --> 00:12:54,104
