think he's had plastic surgery!

119
00:14:45,918 --> 00:14:47,180
Dong-gun?

120
00:14:49,822 --> 00:14:51,187
Dong-gun!

121
00:14:53,125 --> 00:14:54,592
Dong-gun!

122
00:15:09,642 --> 00:15:11,109
