214
00:24:18,423 --> 00:24:22,985
Well... let me think.
Where could he be?

215
00:24:23,128 --> 00:24:25,392
Maybe, probably...

216
00:24:26,031 --> 00:24:29,000
- He's in Hawaii.
- Hawaii? Why?

217
00:24:29,134 --> 00:24:30,897
