the others here 'cause...

241
00:26:54,245 --> 00:26:55,405
you're not here.

242
00:26:56,147 --> 00:26:59,878
Be patient, sweetheart,
I'll give you the greatest gift

243
00:27:00,018 --> 00:27:03,181
for your birthday

244
00:27:06,124 --> 00:27:09,491
