to learn to write.

250
00:27:34,819 --> 00:27:37,379
I'll be there by the time

251
00:27:38,023 --> 00:27:41,481
you've done your homework!

252
00:28:07,519 --> 00:28:08,781
Hae-joo!

253
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:11,384
You can see, can't you?

254
00:28:11,723 --> 00:28:14,692
